{"tid":1934413,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先我當街當巷一巴車落男朋友到","createTime":"2020-03-20T02:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T21:33:12.000Z","uid":38293,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dd098b9e00c84f60c52e645a8537d55707ffe666","tid":1934413,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T02:32:46.000Z","msg":"我真係好心痛<br />\n自問係新時代獨立型女士<br />\n身邊啲JM都好仰慕我<br />\n<br />\n講返正題先<br />\n其實我同男朋友已經有一星期<br />\n我發覺佢係一個好唔識照顧女性嘅男人<br />\n佢應該稱唔上男人<br />\n點解我咁講？<br />\n今日同佢相識一週 咁緊係要拍拖㗎啦<br />\n頭先見面之前我特登整甩條鞋帶<br />\n見面嗰時佢居然完全冇反應完全冇留意過我甩鞋帶<br />\n嗰刻我已經有少少嬲嬲哋<br />\n不過算 我畀一次機會佢<br />\n行咗一分鐘 佢都仲未留意到 好 已經係我嘅極限<br />\n我即刻當眾大巴大巴咁車落去佢度<br />\n其實我都好心痛 點解佢連哩啲細節位都留意唔到？<br />\n仲叫我點樣同佢有將來？<br />\n所以我當下再同佢講我地都係分開下冷靜下"},{"pid":"fb864b6ca5671c467aa5aba4c877955dae4f22e7","tid":1934413,"uid":136738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T02:33:10.000Z","msg":"Sis你真係好勇敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2167fee814a571f65bbffb870582e6ca98169f18","tid":1934413,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fb864b6ca5671c467aa5aba4c877955dae4f22e7","tid":1934413,"uid":136738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T02:33:10.000Z","msg":"Sis你真係好勇敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T02:33:47.000Z","msg":"我真係好傷心"},{"pid":"9b50e73a0e9991e3865dcdb24c98d75f16596749","tid":1934413,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T02:33:56.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"a5ea7785c58623e69b1832aa5b3c34f7c4c7ea77","tid":1934413,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b50e73a0e9991e3865dcdb24c98d75f16596749","tid":1934413,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T02:33:56.000Z","msg":"2/10"